Package cscie55.hw3

This package contains the solution for homework # 3 for the "Java for Distributed Computing" course at Harvard Extension School, Fall 2013.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Building
    The building class simulates a multi-story building with multiple elevators.
    Elevator
    The Elevator class simulates an elevator for a multi-story building.
    Floor
    The Floor class represents a floor in a multi-story building for the Application.
    Passenger
    This class represents a passenger located either inside the elevator or at any floor inside the multi-story building of the Elevator application.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ElevatorDirection
    Enumeration that distinguishes the currentDirection of each elevator in the Elevators' Application.
    ElevatorStatus
    Enumeration that distinguishes the status of each elevator in the Elevator application.
    PassengerStatus
    Enumeration that indicates the status of each passenger in the Elevator application.
